  return value + index;
});

console.log(result);  // [10, 21, 32]

ðŸ‘‰ Each value got incremented by its index.


---

ðŸš€ Quick Summary

Concept	Description

.map()	Creates a new array by transforming every element
Returns	A new array (same length)
Original array	Never modified
Callback args	(element, index, array)
Common use	Calculating or formatting data



---

âœ… Bonus â€” Short arrow syntax

You can shorten this:

